" href="https://www.engadget.com/hbo-max-amazon-prime-video-channels-143851389.html">最大限度</a></ins>.</p><p> Amazon Prime Video 目前单独或作为 Amazon Prime 会员资格的一部分每月收费 8.99 美元。相比之下，Netflix 的标准计划每月收费 9.99 美元，可以解锁高清视频、一次两个屏幕和离线下载。这<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/netflix-basic-with-ads-price-release-date-174526317.html">公司的广告支持层</a></ins>每月 6.99 美元，取消离线下载。目前尚不清楚亚马逊何时计划推出这种广告支持计划或定价可能是什么样子，但它应该有助于降低那些希望订阅亚马逊 Prime Video 且不介意广告的人的成本。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/amazon-is-reportedly-planning-an-ad-supported-tier-for-prime-video-201032287.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/amazon-is-reportedly-planning-an-ad-supported-tier-for-prime-video-201032287.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> e70a2800-6fcf-4403-9101-5437538cbd23</guid><dc:creator>曹彼得</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Wed, 07 Jun 2023 20:10:32 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686168633</ingested><modified> 2023-06-07T20:10:38+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Peter Cao]]></category><media:content height="2668" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-03/7dd1d080-a611-11ec-a5c4-ff85e84157ff" width="4000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2668" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-03/7dd1d080-a611-11ec-a5c